OL,3,CResident says Jersey housing law
OL,4,C'allows abuse to continue'
OL,6,FA woman who says she was in an abusive
OL,7,Frelationship is calling for leniency
OL,8,Fand compassion when it comes to
OL,9,Fhousing laws.
OL,11,F'Rachel', not her real name, tells ITV
OL,12,FNews that she filed for divorce in
OL,13,F2023 after years of alleged emotional
OL,14,Fand physical abuse.
OL,16,FShe recounts one instance: "He comes
OL,17,Fin, locks the door, turns on the
OL,18,Flight, drags me out of bed by the foot
OL,19,Fand our three-year-old wakes up
OL,20,Fscreaming. So he starts slapping me
OL,21,Funtil I lose my orientation."
