OL,3,CResident says Jersey housing law
OL,4,C'allows abuse to continue'
OL,6,FRachel now works full-time but all her
OL,7,Fmoney is tied up in assets her husband
OL,8,Fcontrols.
OL,10,FCurrently, when only one person has
OL,11,Fentitled status, their partner can
OL,12,Flive with them in qualified housing
OL,13,Fbut he left, leaving her and her sons
OL,14,Fwithout residential status as they
OL,15,Fhave only been living in the island
OL,16,Fsince 2019.
OL,18,FShe wants more to be done to help
OL,19,Fpeople who find themselves in a
OL,20,Fsituation like this.
