OL,3,CResident says Jersey housing law
OL,4,C'allows abuse to continue'
OL,6,FRachel explains: "I've got to get
OL,7,Fthrough this day by day. The local
OL,8,Flaws, not only do they not make it
OL,9,Feasier considering my situation, they
OL,10,Factually make it harder and they allow
OL,11,Fthe abuser to continue their abuse."
OL,13,FJersey's Housing Minister, Deputy Sam
OL,14,FMezec, adds: "I've come across cases
OL,15,Flike this before where people in
OL,16,Freally difficult situations have found
OL,17,Fthemselves without proper housing
OL,18,Fstatus to enable them to get the right
OL,19,Fkind of home that they need and these
OL,20,Fare sometimes households with children
OL,21,Fin as well.
