OL,6,F"It seems to me quite arbitrary that
OL,7,Fpeople can be prevented from getting
OL,8,Fthe homes they need and the rules are
OL,9,Fstopping them from doing that."
OL,11,FRachel has now contacted Jersey's
OL,12,FChief Minister, Deputy Lyndon Farnham,
OL,13,Fwho does, unlike the Housing Minister,
OL,14,Fhave the power to intervene on
OL,15,Fhardship grounds in exceptional cases.
