OL,6,FIn response, Deputy Carina Alves,
OL,7,FAssistant Minister to the Chief
OL,8,FMinister, says: "The Council of
OL,9,FMinisters cannot comment on individual
OL,10,Fcases, but will always act to support
OL,11,Fvictims of domestic abuse.
OL,13,F"The Social Security Minister has
OL,14,Flaunched a new scheme that provides 13
OL,15,Fweeks of financial support to domestic
OL,16,Fabuse victims, irrespective of a
OL,17,Fperson's residency or financial means.
